{"tid":305922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"ZCash交流區","createTime":"2017-07-02T06:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T06:22:42.000Z","uid":126128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"402ee36c023e998935a8dc765f3f59f3f7d23be9","tid":305922,"uid":126128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"小弟做左CD Rom好多年，今日初入連登多多指教<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，冇幾耐之前小弟開始挖礦( ZCash)，收入唔錯，諗住係度同各位巴打交流下挖礦心得。<br />\n<br />\n挖ZCash用EWBF黎挖是常識吧，只不過呢款Miner收得我2%稅，但交唔到貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。計速度佢係快，但係最大問題係炒左唔識重開。開頭小弟用EWBF果陣半夜炒左，成晚冇挖到，損失慘重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到我用佢挖礦完全唔敢超頻，返工要成日扮去廁所teamviewer返去check有冇炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於小弟個朋友(利申︰我朋友不是我)睇唔過眼，寫左個ZCash Miner，效率同EWBF一樣。而最大特色係，EWBF個程式炒左就停，佢炒左重開。以後唔洗扮腎虧個個鐘去廁所check有冇炒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且仲有UI，入左個address揀左pool後一鍵採礦，唔洗對住個BAT打 command落param鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，佢同巿面既miner( 例如 EWBF )一樣，會抽2%稅。<br />\n<br />\n如果對個Miner有任何意見，可以係度提出，我會轉達俾佢知<br />\n<br />\nDownload Link:  <a href=\"https://github.com/xinzec/miner_gui\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fxinzec%2Fminer_gui&d=yEuBrdW%2FqhIqLpDDj4aaaozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bd88ec3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/xinzec/miner_gui</a>"}]}